	<h1 class="title">小黄人是如何占领洛杉矶，以及整个世界的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/99238/small/99238.jpg?1435570983" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙今泾 温欣语</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-13 14:08:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11999/medium/11999.png?1436755007" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


